<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="17Apr1932"><font color="red">17 April 1932</font> <i>BLHW</i> (to Harriet Weaver, typed): I am dictating this to Gilbert in his flat. I gave up my Passy flat on the 8th, but had to remain on till this morning &hellip; This morning we all went to the Gare du Nord &hellip; Lucia had a violent hysterical attack &hellip; the only thing to be done is abandon all attempt to keep up a residence in London &hellip; I have been working practically all day for some time past </div>
